item.description:
下面这个脚本提供了etcdctl连接etcd所需要的断点、证书相关的信息, 能快速或许并调用命令查看, 这个脚本需要在master节点上执行:
#!/bin/bash ENDPOINTS=$(pgrep kube-apiserver | grep -P &#39;etcd-servers=(.*?)\s&#39; -o | awk -F= &#39;{print $2}&#39;) CACERT=$(pgrep kube-apiserver | grep -P &#39;etcd-cafile=(.*?)\s&#39; -o | awk -F= &#39;{print $2}&#39;) CERT=$(pgrep kube-apiserver | grep -P &#39;etcd-certfile=(.*?)\s&#39; -o | awk -F= &#39;{print $2}&#39;) KEY=$(pgrep kube-apiserver | grep -P &#39;etcd-keyfile=(.*?)\s&#39; -o | awk -F= &#39;{print $2}&#39;) ETCDCTL_API=3 etcdctl --endpoints=&#34;$ENDPOINTS&#34; --cacert=&#34;$CACERT&#34; --key=&#34;$KEY&#34; --cert=&#34;$CERT&#34; &#34;$@&#34; 或者, 使用这个命令一键下载脚本:
curl -o ./etcdctl.sh https://blog.llaoj.cn/posts/2208/kubernetes-etcdctl-usage/etcdctl.sh / &amp;&amp; chmod +x .
